{"tid":264322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又搵腦魔着數？","createTime":"2017-05-30T17:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T16:52:27.000Z","uid":9677,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9bbd8067531583c1bbb9dcfe59ed4c808ee6bb","tid":264322,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/005824_2711cb1ac6d162a6155b8b0874ed2dc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F005824_2711cb1ac6d162a6155b8b0874ed2dc6.jpg&h=93178c8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要有埋潮文卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哇哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/010311_54c878f05c20c5bae04f5745976ba96a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F010311_54c878f05c20c5bae04f5745976ba96a.jpg&h=7963cf71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32c8468c71be2343c552c07efc585762130e225f","tid":264322,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:26:19.000Z","msg":"你申請個版權咪可以告鳩佢地囉<br />\n係度眼紅無意思"},{"pid":"1c954771f4fe3a422a80adb4b7ab1aa90382039b","tid":264322,"uid":9677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你申請個版權咪可以告鳩佢地囉<br />\n係度眼紅無意思</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係你覺得將人哋原創嘅嘢，當係自己嘅嘢拎出黎賣 就係無錯？<br />\n<br />\n老實講我覺得呢種行為簡直係無賴，應該係世界上最厚面皮嘅人先會做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97809bd2f5f1069196204372f37635a2444c15b5","tid":264322,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你申請個版權咪可以告鳩佢地囉<br />\n係度眼紅無意思</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我冇喺度眼紅，因為即使佢賺唔賺都唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且梗係將呢啲咁有熱心推廣LIHKG IG店要好好表揚下啦<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你哋班非原創狗應該多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為多得我幫你地宣傳"},{"pid":"77912e7d03586b6c7730577e8e99a3987d393e56","tid":264322,"uid":9677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/01/005212_234550cc37c751a288ca9deb72591856.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F01%2F005212_234550cc37c751a288ca9deb72591856.jpg&h=51ac4711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哇，屌你"}]}